item.title: CVE-2022-4636|2024-08-03T01:48:39.612Z -- black%20box -- kvm%20acr1020a-t
item.description: Black Box KVM Firmware version 3.4.31307 on models ACR1000A-R-R2, ACR1000A-T-R2, ACR1002A-T, ACR1002A-R, and ACR1020A-T is vulnerable to path traversal, which may allow an attacker to steal user credentials and other sensitive information through local file inclusion.
